articles.author: Kevin Buckland
articles.title: Asian stocks climb on Wall Street lead; yuan, euro sag - Reuters
articles.description: Asian stocks jumped on Tuesday led by an outperforming tech sector following record highs on Wall Street overnight, while the dollar recovered lost ground against major rivals as traders weighed the outlook for U.S. interest rates.

articles.title: Researchers finally identify the ocean’s “mystery mollusk” - Ars Technica
articles.description: It’s a nudibranch, but so distantly related that it gets its own phylogenetic family.
